Personal Style:
David's personal style reflects his down-to-earth and practical approach to life. He favors comfortable, durable clothing that can withstand the demands of his active lifestyle. His wardrobe consists primarily of casual, versatile pieces, such as jeans, t-shirts, and sturdy boots. David values function over fashion and aims to present a relatable, approachable image to the communities he serves.

